{"tid":477753,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雖然李克勤唱歌感情係不足，但技巧上絕對能夠與學友平排！","createTime":"2017-11-23T10:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T11:45:12.000Z","uid":49388,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2a5a3630ac53898d310ad9a803b715f13f0518c1","tid":477753,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T10:31:32.000Z","msg":"咪話我成日追撃佢唔讚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢唱歌絕都有可取之處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由其岩岩咸魚番生個三年，大概01至03年<br />\n<br />\n佢既功力可以由港樂克勤01演唱會中表露無遺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個陣聲底薄得黎又清，真音愈高愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，依家聲沉又沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有當時唱歌好似唔洗用力咁，真音上去係唔需要爆，係極之輕鬆，當食生菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n發聲共鳴位置多，加上氣息強，令到有足夠既空間放大聲音，令穿透力強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n流𣈱度極佳，字與字之間極之細膩，live比依家再穩定多起碼5成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n音準極盡完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咬字非常清析，隨左羅文外之後就係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聲底技巧根本完美。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打後既演奏廰系列已經唔係個回事...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以唱歌技巧計算，真係可以同張學友平排，咬字音準穩定學友都未必及李生，以當時計算，技巧上絕對係SS級！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\